Communication:
Use NRF24L01 Transceiver for Communication Between Control and Car

Actuators:
	2 - Microservo motors for wheel movements on car
	2 - Microservo motors for pan tilt movements
	1- Laser or other static actuating sensor for data collection 
	Transceiver set for communication
 
Sensors:
	Accelerometer for directional hand movements 
	Button for Laser Light 	
  Touch Sensor for switch between movement and pan/tilt control

Schematics
	Glove
	Robot Chassis
	Two Wheels
	Pan Tilt Kit 
	Laser


Process: 
  Glove controls movement
  Switch with flex sensor
  Led tells mode
  Button press triggers laser

Functions and Program Control
